{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Projection/PrjCoordSysType/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><br>\n在 SuperMap iDesktop 中，数据的坐标系分为三类：平面坐标系、地理坐标系、投影坐标系。</p>\n<h3 id=\"平面坐标系\"><a href=\"#%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"PlaneCoordSysDia.htm\">平面坐标系</a></h3>\n<p>一般用来作为与地理位置无关的数据的坐标参考，也是默认新建数据的坐标参考，如 CAD\n设计图、纸质地图扫描后的图片、与地理位置无关的示意图等。平面坐标系是一个二维坐标系，原点坐标为（0，0），数据中每一个点的坐标是由其距水平和垂直的 X 轴和\nY 轴的距离确定。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/48f836387dc28c7dbea9ff32f94c1d2f/308c1/Prj_CS_Type_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 338px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 74.2603550295858%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Prj CS Type 1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/48f836387dc28c7dbea9ff32f94c1d2f/308c1/Prj_CS_Type_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/48f836387dc28c7dbea9ff32f94c1d2f/6a467/Prj_CS_Type_1.png 210w,\n/static/48f836387dc28c7dbea9ff32f94c1d2f/308c1/Prj_CS_Type_1.png 338w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      </p>\n<h3 id=\"地理坐标系\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"GeoCoordSysDia.htm\">地理坐标系</a></h3>\n<p>使用经纬度坐标来表示椭球上任意一点的坐标。地理坐标系中，通常包含对水平基准、中央子午线和角度单位的定义。常用的地理坐标系如：WGS\n1984、Beijing1954、Clarke 1866 等。例如，Google Earth 上的 KML 数据，全球定位系统采集的数据，都是以 WGS\n1984 为坐标系的。大地测量获取的控制点坐标以西安80或 Beijing 1954为坐标系。图为 WGS 1984 坐标系的世界地图。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7bc7a6127f3936a6cd38a2c7fcf55a4a/37e1f/Prj_CS_Type_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 474px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.540084388185655%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Prj CS Type 2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7bc7a6127f3936a6cd38a2c7fcf55a4a/37e1f/Prj_CS_Type_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7bc7a6127f3936a6cd38a2c7fcf55a4a/6a467/Prj_CS_Type_2.png 210w,\n/static/7bc7a6127f3936a6cd38a2c7fcf55a4a/635b1/Prj_CS_Type_2.png 420w,\n/static/7bc7a6127f3936a6cd38a2c7fcf55a4a/37e1f/Prj_CS_Type_2.png 474w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      </p>\n<h3 id=\"投影坐标系\"><a href=\"#%E6%8A%95%E5%BD%B1%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"PrjCoordSysDia.htm\">投影坐标系</a></h3>\n<p>通过某种投影方式和投影类型，将椭球上的任意一点投影到平面上。使用二维平面坐标(X、Y）\n来表示点线面地物的位置。投影坐标系中，通常包含对地理坐标系、地图投影、投影参数及距离单位的定义。常用的投影坐标系例如：Gauss\nKruger、Albers、Lambert、Robinson\n等。一般，经过投影的地理数据，可进行地图量算、各种空间分析、制图表达等。例如，我国基本比例尺地形图中，1：100万地形图采用 Lambert\n投影，其余大部分都采用了高斯-\n克吕格6°带或者3°带投影。而城市规划中用到的大比例尺地图，如1：500，1：1000等的道路施工图、建筑设计图等多采用平面坐标系。图为原 WGS\n1984坐标系的世界地图进行了 Robinson 投影。<br>\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/75b9e2f4c399ac43ea9603709bd3996c/be49d/Prj_CS_Type_3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 412px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 52.9126213592233%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Prj CS Type 3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/75b9e2f4c399ac43ea9603709bd3996c/be49d/Prj_CS_Type_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/75b9e2f4c399ac43ea9603709bd3996c/6a467/Prj_CS_Type_3.png 210w,\n/static/75b9e2f4c399ac43ea9603709bd3996c/be49d/Prj_CS_Type_3.png 412w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 412px) 100vw, 412px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      </p>","frontmatter":{"title":"坐标系的类型","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\DataProcessing\\Projection\\PrjCoordSysType.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Projection/PrjCoordSysType/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Projection/PrjCoordSysType/"}}}